g\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F69usdxa.png&h=afc4f3f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n堅持五大訴求 拒絕警黑勾結<br />\n<br />\n1. 徹底撤回逃犯修訂條例<br />\n2. 釋放所有因反送中被捕人士並承諾永不追究<br />\n3. 撤回612暴動定性<br />\n4. 追究警察濫權濫暴(包括721元朗官警黑勾結事件)，成立獨立調查委員會<br />\n5. 立即實行雙普選"},{"pid":"fb9e9b6fe970ec641d0abfdbcf1b69795ebcc8be","tid":1384912,"uid":9128,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T03:42:12.000Z","msg":"坐uo<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"675858a44f11a644664427b86db8dde1863b9f2d","tid":1384912,"uid":253880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T03:42:42.000Z","msg":"今年唔係又去西貢咩?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55bfd0db1c234c969d679adefe50aff6fc452d12","tid":1384912,"uid":259530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T03:43:19.000Z","msg":"98"},{"pid":"db9fd0b1a473266f327b0c052f656a1556e6ce3d","tid":1384912,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T03:48:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cba796da4cd68e8a0c3ba6a338245892b8489324","tid":1384912,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb9e9b6fe970ec641d0abfdbcf1b69795ebcc8be","tid":1384912,"uid":9128,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T03:42:12.000Z","msg":"坐uo<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T03:48:27.000Z","msg":"熊本得UO(好似係）"},{"pid":"190c37939d2eefa7190408390aa50e1da56517ae","tid":1384912,"uid":205188,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T03:49:50.000Z","msg":"有無黃絲港姐"},{"pid":"9a1d4d0e46991a4c120e14222e57cc6e080cc667","tid":1384912,"uid":6528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T03:50:04.000Z","msg":"全民8月5曰大罷工！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雙普選應要排最頭！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n全民黑衫、口罩同頭盔，返工返學行街，唔擺工既日子一齊做，將抗爭帶入生活，保護示威者<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1379839\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1379839</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！<br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n想比更多人知道其實而家呢一刻基本上得番香港獨立呢條路，<br />\n我知好多人未準備好，我知而家急唔黎。<br />\n但係想大家思考下，種下一個思想，唔好屌我住。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家就算有真普選其實都係under中共！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁唔通去到2047再抗爭過咩，西方國家都出唔到手幫你地。<br />\n因為白紙黑字寫明50年，西方國家唔好話出手，連發聲既正當性都冇啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可能好多前人都係到諗點解英國當時唔寫999年！<br />\n可能好多我地呢代既諗點解上一代冇去抗爭！<br />\n可能好多下一代係2047係到諗點解我地唔直接爭取獨立！！！<br />\n<br />\n2047到時只會都係變返中國，仲要一下子就變，一定好多人接受唔到。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所有問題去到最後只會追究到主權問題，希望大家思考下。<br />\n今次搞到咁大真係最後一次反擊同最大力量。<br />\n<br />\nBTW，五大訴求，缺一不可！<br />\n雙普選應要排最頭"},{"pid":"d9d012728deea7d4828cae35ef28099f7906a795","tid":1384912,"uid":113630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T04:42:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1e83ef6ab9386b3d46e0359cdeff9c0319c1599a","tid":1384912,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T04:44:46.000Z","msg":"上次九展見唔到面 今次機會黎喇"}]}